title: Nvidia Geforce 920M
body: I have got a new pc i7 /Nvidia Geforce 920m but my FPS is Fixed on 60 pls help you can contact me on skype **[REDACTED]**

replies.body:
I had to remove your skype name because that information is pretty sensitive and could cause security issues for you. 

Regarding your FPS issue, this is likely caused by the Windows 10 update that enabled *game DVR* in the Windows Game Bar. I strongly recommend you disable the game bar with [this guide](http://www.tenforums.com/tutorials/8637-game-bar-turn-off-windows-10-a.html) to see if it was causing the issue.

Let me know if this helped.

In that case, since those steps didn't work, this may be caused by a driver issue or windows power settings. I recommend working through the common solutions we've consolidated in our [FPS troubleshooting guide](https://support.riotgames.com/hc/en-us/articles/201752684-Low-Frame-Rate-FPS-Troubleshooting) as a next step.

Let me know if those steps caused any change for you.

We'll need to take a deep look at your system logs to determine what is causing this. For us to do this, we'll need you to run a set of logs using our [Hextech Tool](https://support.riotgames.com/hc/en-us/articles/224826367), then attach them to a [support ticket](https://support.riotgames.com/hc/en-us/requests/new) request.

Let me know if you have any questions.
